[
    {
        "text": "Hi, and welcome back to engVid.",
        "start": 0.64,
        "duration": 1.72
    },
    {
        "text": "Today we have a really special lesson planned\nfor you.",
        "start": 2.36,
        "duration": 2.8
    },
    {
        "text": "In this lesson, you'll learn how to wish somebody\nin person, or in an email, or on Facebook",
        "start": 5.16,
        "duration": 7.77
    },
    {
        "text": "during the happy and sad occasions of our\nlives.",
        "start": 12.93,
        "duration": 3.47
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 16.4,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, actually, I've learned different languages;\nand even though sometimes you learn all kinds",
        "start": 17.4,
        "duration": 4.23
    },
    {
        "text": "of complex words and all kinds of difficult\nthings, sometimes it's hardest to say the",
        "start": 21.63,
        "duration": 5.159
    },
    {
        "text": "simplest wishes and greetings in the natural\nway that they should flow when somebody tells",
        "start": 26.789,
        "duration": 6.171
    },
    {
        "text": "you good news or bad news.",
        "start": 32.96,
        "duration": 2.25
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 35.21,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "So, this is to review, in case you don't know,\nand there may be some situations where you're",
        "start": 36.21,
        "duration": 6.18
    },
    {
        "text": "not...",
        "start": 42.39,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Not really sure at all what to say.",
        "start": 43.39,
        "duration": 1.579
    },
    {
        "text": "So, try to do this quickly with me.",
        "start": 44.969,
        "duration": 2.471
    },
    {
        "text": "I'm going to give you a situation, and you\ntell me quickly: What do you say to a person",
        "start": 47.44,
        "duration": 4.52
    },
    {
        "text": "in that situation?",
        "start": 51.96,
        "duration": 1.239
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, some of them are going to be pretty obvious,\nand some maybe not.",
        "start": 53.199,
        "duration": 3.311
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 56.51,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Are you ready?",
        "start": 57.51,
        "duration": 1.08
    },
    {
        "text": "Let's get started.",
        "start": 58.59,
        "duration": 1.5
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 60.09,
        "duration": 1.059
    },
    {
        "text": "What do you to say to someone on their birthday?",
        "start": 61.149,
        "duration": 2.281
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Happy birthday.\"",
        "start": 63.43,
        "duration": 1.73
    },
    {
        "text": "Good.",
        "start": 65.16,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, as I ask you, if you want or you need\nmore time, then just pause and say it.",
        "start": 66.16,
        "duration": 6.91
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 73.07,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "But, really, we're going to do this quite\nfast.",
        "start": 74.07,
        "duration": 1.92
    },
    {
        "text": "So, on a birthday we say: \"Happy birthday.\"",
        "start": 75.99,
        "duration": 4.18
    },
    {
        "text": "Later I'll tell you what else you can write\nbesides: \"Happy birthday.\"",
        "start": 80.17,
        "duration": 4.489
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 84.659,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Your friend has a job interview.",
        "start": 85.659,
        "duration": 2.151
    },
    {
        "text": "Before they go for the job interview, what\ndo you say?",
        "start": 87.81,
        "duration": 3.25
    },
    {
        "text": "There are a number of possibilities, here,\nbut tell me something quickly.",
        "start": 91.06,
        "duration": 5.01
    },
    {
        "text": "You can say: \"Good luck.\"",
        "start": 96.07,
        "duration": 1.82
    },
    {
        "text": "You could say: \"All the best.\"",
        "start": 97.89,
        "duration": 2.28
    },
    {
        "text": "All right?",
        "start": 100.17,
        "duration": 1.44
    },
    {
        "text": "Good.",
        "start": 101.61,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "It's your friend's anniversary, what do you\nsay to them?",
        "start": 102.61,
        "duration": 4.18
    },
    {
        "text": "You say: \"Happy anniversary.\"",
        "start": 106.79,
        "duration": 2.55
    },
    {
        "text": "Yes, that works.",
        "start": 109.34,
        "duration": 1.4
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 110.74,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "You can also say: \"Congratulations\", but:\n\"Happy anniversary\" is fine.",
        "start": 111.74,
        "duration": 4.72
    },
    {
        "text": "It's January 1st and you see a friend, what\ndo you say to him?",
        "start": 116.46,
        "duration": 4.87
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Happy New Year.\"",
        "start": 121.33,
        "duration": 3.039
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 124.369,
        "duration": 1.011
    },
    {
        "text": "Good.",
        "start": 125.38,
        "duration": 1.019
    },
    {
        "text": "It's somebody's wedding day, what do you say\nto them?",
        "start": 126.399,
        "duration": 5.471
    },
    {
        "text": "Usually we just say: \"Congratulations.\"",
        "start": 131.87,
        "duration": 2.11
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 133.98,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Again, later I'll tell you what else you can\nsay after that basic word, but you at least",
        "start": 134.98,
        "duration": 5.06
    },
    {
        "text": "want to get the basic words out of your mouth.",
        "start": 140.04,
        "duration": 2.75
    },
    {
        "text": "Right?",
        "start": 142.79,
        "duration": 1.01
    },
    {
        "text": "Good.",
        "start": 143.8,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, we don't always do this, but often we\ndo say something before someone's about to",
        "start": 144.8,
        "duration": 7.45
    },
    {
        "text": "eat, like, a nice meal or something like that.",
        "start": 152.25,
        "duration": 3.42
    },
    {
        "text": "And the strange part is we say something in\nFrench because we don't actually have something",
        "start": 155.67,
        "duration": 5.58
    },
    {
        "text": "in English to say before you're about to sit\ndown to eat a nice meal.",
        "start": 161.25,
        "duration": 4.44
    },
    {
        "text": "So, have you heard what people say before\nsomeone is about to eat a nice, fancy meal?",
        "start": 165.69,
        "duration": 6.519
    },
    {
        "text": "Have you heard?",
        "start": 172.209,
        "duration": 1.271
    },
    {
        "text": "We say: \"Bon appétit\", which in French\nmeans: \"Good appetite.\"",
        "start": 173.48,
        "duration": 4.5
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 177.98,
        "duration": 1.14
    },
    {
        "text": "So, that's something for you to learn.",
        "start": 179.12,
        "duration": 2.4
    },
    {
        "text": "All right?",
        "start": 181.52,
        "duration": 2.249
    },
    {
        "text": "Your friend tells you that she's pregnant,\nand you say: \"Congratulations.\"",
        "start": 183.769,
        "duration": 5.431
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 189.2,
        "duration": 1.53
    },
    {
        "text": "Next, someone is introduced to you.",
        "start": 190.73,
        "duration": 3.039
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 193.769,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "So, what do you say to them?",
        "start": 194.769,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "You put out your hand and you say: \"Nice to\nmeet you.\"",
        "start": 195.769,
        "duration": 3.241
    },
    {
        "text": "By the way, depending on the culture and the\nsituation, you don't always put out your hand",
        "start": 199.01,
        "duration": 3.839
    },
    {
        "text": "for...",
        "start": 202.849,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "To shake hands, but what you say is: \"Nice\nto meet you.\"",
        "start": 203.849,
        "duration": 3.81
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 207.659,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Good.",
        "start": 208.659,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "If someone has helped you a lot through a\ndifficult situation, or with a project, something",
        "start": 209.659,
        "duration": 5.171
    },
    {
        "text": "at work, something at home, what do you say\nto someone who has helped you?",
        "start": 214.83,
        "duration": 4.579
    },
    {
        "text": "You say: \"Thank you.\"",
        "start": 219.409,
        "duration": 3.961
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 223.37,
        "duration": 1.27
    },
    {
        "text": "This one you may or may not know if you haven't\nbeen in this situation.",
        "start": 224.64,
        "duration": 3.84
    },
    {
        "text": "Somebody loses someone that they love-that\nmeans someone in their family passes away",
        "start": 228.48,
        "duration": 3.86
    },
    {
        "text": "or dies-what are you supposed to say to them?",
        "start": 232.34,
        "duration": 3.27
    },
    {
        "text": "Well, there are a few possibilities.",
        "start": 235.61,
        "duration": 2.01
    },
    {
        "text": "So, you could say: \"My condolences.\"",
        "start": 237.62,
        "duration": 3.869
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 241.489,
        "duration": 1.121
    },
    {
        "text": "The word is: \"condolences\".",
        "start": 242.61,
        "duration": 2.099
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 244.709,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Please accept my condolences.\"",
        "start": 245.709,
        "duration": 2.171
    },
    {
        "text": "Or: \"I'm very sorry to hear that.\"",
        "start": 247.88,
        "duration": 2.87
    },
    {
        "text": "If you can't remember the word \"condolences\"\nor you feel it's hard to pronounce or something,",
        "start": 250.75,
        "duration": 4.44
    },
    {
        "text": "just say: \"I'm very sorry to hear that.",
        "start": 255.19,
        "duration": 2.73
    },
    {
        "text": "I'm very sorry for your loss.\"",
        "start": 257.92,
        "duration": 2.47
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 260.39,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, in case you're not catching exactly what\nI'm saying, what you can do during this lesson",
        "start": 261.39,
        "duration": 7.25
    },
    {
        "text": "is to turn on the captions, which we have,\nand there you'll see these words that I'm",
        "start": 268.64,
        "duration": 4.96
    },
    {
        "text": "saying written down.",
        "start": 273.6,
        "duration": 2.26
    },
    {
        "text": "And if there's anything you don't know, then\nyou could write them down for yourself, which",
        "start": 275.86,
        "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
        "text": "is also a very good way for you to remember.",
        "start": 279.3,
        "duration": 2.55
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 281.85,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "So, there, you'll be able to write down, like:\n\"Condolences\", \"Congratulations\", exactly",
        "start": 282.85,
        "duration": 5.04
    },
    {
        "text": "how to spell and write these words.",
        "start": 287.89,
        "duration": 2.71
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 290.6,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Let's continue.",
        "start": 291.6,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Did you know or did you notice that in English\nwhen someone sneezes, we often say something",
        "start": 292.6,
        "duration": 6.85
    },
    {
        "text": "to them?",
        "start": 299.45,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Do you know what that is?",
        "start": 300.45,
        "duration": 1.67
    },
    {
        "text": "It's: \"Bless you.\"",
        "start": 302.12,
        "duration": 2.01
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 304.13,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "All right.",
        "start": 305.13,
        "duration": 1.01
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Bless you.\"",
        "start": 306.14,
        "duration": 1.34
    },
    {
        "text": "All right.",
        "start": 307.48,
        "duration": 1.34
    },
    {
        "text": "That actually comes from an earlier time because\nwhen somebody sneezed in the olden days, it",
        "start": 308.82,
        "duration": 5.49
    },
    {
        "text": "meant they were unwell and they were really\nnot...",
        "start": 314.31,
        "duration": 2.75
    },
    {
        "text": "You were worried about them and you didn't\nwant them to die or anything like that, so",
        "start": 317.06,
        "duration": 5.94
    },
    {
        "text": "you blessed them so that they got back to\ngood health.",
        "start": 323.0,
        "duration": 3.12
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 326.12,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "That's it.",
        "start": 327.12,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "All right.",
        "start": 328.12,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "You heard that someone got a job, so what\ndo you say?",
        "start": 329.12,
        "duration": 2.87
    },
    {
        "text": "You say: \"Congratulations.\"",
        "start": 331.99,
        "duration": 2.49
    },
    {
        "text": "Good.",
        "start": 334.48,
        "duration": 1.23
    },
    {
        "text": "You're trying to walk but somebody's in your\nway, so what do you say to them?",
        "start": 335.71,
        "duration": 4.85
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Excuse me.\"",
        "start": 340.56,
        "duration": 1.62
    },
    {
        "text": "Right.",
        "start": 342.18,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Good.",
        "start": 343.18,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 344.18,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "You heard that your friend had a baby, and\nyou say: \"Congratulations.\"",
        "start": 345.18,
        "duration": 4.37
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 349.55,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Good.",
        "start": 350.55,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Afterwards I'll tell you what you can say\nafter: \"Congratulations.\"",
        "start": 351.55,
        "duration": 2.75
    },
    {
        "text": "All right.",
        "start": 354.3,
        "duration": 1.53
    },
    {
        "text": "You're introduced to someone, what do you\nsay?",
        "start": 355.83,
        "duration": 2.82
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Nice to meet you.\"",
        "start": 358.65,
        "duration": 1.78
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 360.43,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Again, with or without the handshake.",
        "start": 361.43,
        "duration": 3.06
    },
    {
        "text": "Someone passes an exam.",
        "start": 364.49,
        "duration": 1.26
    },
    {
        "text": "Your friend tells you: \"Oh, I passed the exam\",\nand you say: \"Congratulations.\"",
        "start": 365.75,
        "duration": 4.19
    },
    {
        "text": "All right?",
        "start": 369.94,
        "duration": 1.46
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, if your friend is going for the exam\nand you meet them before, what could you say?",
        "start": 371.4,
        "duration": 5.97
    },
    {
        "text": "You could say: \"All the best.",
        "start": 377.37,
        "duration": 2.01
    },
    {
        "text": "Good luck.\"",
        "start": 379.38,
        "duration": 1.16
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 380.54,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Good.",
        "start": 381.54,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Someone's going away on holiday, what can\nyou say to them?",
        "start": 382.54,
        "duration": 3.66
    },
    {
        "text": "Well, here, we don't have, like, a fixed phrase;\nthere are a few possibilities.",
        "start": 386.2,
        "duration": 3.82
    },
    {
        "text": "You can say: \"Have a good holiday.\", \"Have\na great time.\", \"Bon voya-...",
        "start": 390.02,
        "duration": 4.22
    },
    {
        "text": "Bon voyage.",
        "start": 394.24,
        "duration": 2.38
    },
    {
        "text": "Bon voyage.\"",
        "start": 396.62,
        "duration": 1.01
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 397.63,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "That's it - I got it.",
        "start": 398.63,
        "duration": 1.14
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Bon voyage.\"",
        "start": 399.77,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Again, it's French; it's not English, so we\ndo use that, though.",
        "start": 400.77,
        "duration": 5.36
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 406.13,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Next, someone thanks you for something, so\nwhat do you say?",
        "start": 407.13,
        "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
        "text": "They say: \"Thank you.\"",
        "start": 410.57,
        "duration": 1.85
    },
    {
        "text": "You say: \"You're welcome.\"",
        "start": 412.42,
        "duration": 2.6
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 415.02,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "That's the standard thing; there are many\nother possibilities you can say, but usually",
        "start": 416.02,
        "duration": 4.47
    },
    {
        "text": "we say: \"You're welcome.\"",
        "start": 420.49,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 421.49,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Or if you want to go a little bit further,\nyou say: \"My pleasure.\", \"No problem.\"",
        "start": 422.49,
        "duration": 2.63
    },
    {
        "text": "It depends on the formality of the situation\nand what the situation was.",
        "start": 425.12,
        "duration": 5.98
    },
    {
        "text": "Someone raises a glass, say: \"Let's toast\nabout bride and groom.",
        "start": 431.1,
        "duration": 3.84
    },
    {
        "text": "Let's make a toast.\"",
        "start": 434.94,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "So everybody usually says: \"Cheers.\"",
        "start": 435.94,
        "duration": 3.89
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 439.83,
        "duration": 1.25
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Cheers.\"",
        "start": 441.08,
        "duration": 1.25
    },
    {
        "text": "Good.",
        "start": 442.33,
        "duration": 1.25
    },
    {
        "text": "And if you make a mistake, then...",
        "start": 443.58,
        "duration": 3.15
    },
    {
        "text": "Say you forgot someone's birthday, so you\ncall and say: \"I'm sorry.\"",
        "start": 446.73,
        "duration": 4.25
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 450.98,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Good.",
        "start": 451.98,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "\"I'm sorry.\"",
        "start": 452.98,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "All right?",
        "start": 453.98,
        "duration": 1.16
    },
    {
        "text": "So, here you had a lot of words that are...",
        "start": 455.14,
        "duration": 3.6
    },
    {
        "text": "Really should come to you easily, so you need\nto practice them.",
        "start": 458.74,
        "duration": 3.05
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 461.79,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Because life is not about just looking at\nthe board and knowing what to say; life comes",
        "start": 462.79,
        "duration": 4.34
    },
    {
        "text": "at you just like that, right?",
        "start": 467.13,
        "duration": 1.98
    },
    {
        "text": "At random.",
        "start": 469.11,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "That's why I just wrote all kinds of situations;\nsome are good, some are bad, some are sad,",
        "start": 470.11,
        "duration": 3.98
    },
    {
        "text": "some are exciting, whatever - and you have\nto have the answers at the moment.",
        "start": 474.09,
        "duration": 4.51
    },
    {
        "text": "Right?",
        "start": 478.6,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "So, sometimes: \"Congratulations.\", \"I'm sorry.\",\n\"Thank you.\", \"Good luck.\", \"All the best.\"",
        "start": 479.6,
        "duration": 4.9
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 484.5,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "\"My condolences.\", \"Bon voyage.\", \"Bon appétit.\"",
        "start": 485.5,
        "duration": 2.34
    },
    {
        "text": "All of these things, okay?",
        "start": 487.84,
        "duration": 2.39
    },
    {
        "text": "But now let's look a little bit further in\nthe next part what you can say after these",
        "start": 490.23,
        "duration": 5.46
    },
    {
        "text": "basic greetings.",
        "start": 495.69,
        "duration": 1.6
    },
    {
        "text": "Because what I've realized when I was looking\nat Facebook, a lot of people are just writing:",
        "start": 497.29,
        "duration": 3.93
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Happy birthday.\", \"Happy birthday.\", \"Happy\nbirthday.\", \"Happy birthday.\", \"Happy birthday.\"",
        "start": 501.22,
        "duration": 3.29
    },
    {
        "text": "And nobody's saying anything else.",
        "start": 504.51,
        "duration": 2.37
    },
    {
        "text": "So, what else could you say besides that?",
        "start": 506.88,
        "duration": 3.33
    },
    {
        "text": "How can you personalize it?",
        "start": 510.21,
        "duration": 1.72
    },
    {
        "text": "How can you humanize it?",
        "start": 511.93,
        "duration": 1.64
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 513.57,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Let's look at some possibilities.",
        "start": 514.57,
        "duration": 1.5
    },
    {
        "text": "I'll be back in a sec.",
        "start": 516.07,
        "duration": 1.3
    },
    {
        "text": "All right, now let's go over: What are some\nthings you could say after you say: \"Happy",
        "start": 517.37,
        "duration": 5.88
    },
    {
        "text": "birthday\", and some other wishes and greetings?",
        "start": 523.25,
        "duration": 2.37
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 525.62,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "So, here we go.",
        "start": 526.62,
        "duration": 1.75
    },
    {
        "text": "And this is especially useful, as I said,\nif you're writing it.",
        "start": 528.37,
        "duration": 3.33
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 531.7,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "You can also say these things, but especially\nif you're writing an email, or you're writing",
        "start": 532.7,
        "duration": 3.7
    },
    {
        "text": "on Facebook, or you're writing someone a message,\nor you're writing in a greeting card, or you",
        "start": 536.4,
        "duration": 4.731
    },
    {
        "text": "work somewhere and they pass around a greeting\ncard, and you want to write something a little",
        "start": 541.131,
        "duration": 4.029
    },
    {
        "text": "bit different.",
        "start": 545.16,
        "duration": 1.03
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 546.19,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "It's always nice.",
        "start": 547.19,
        "duration": 1.07
    },
    {
        "text": "And also try to think about who that person\nis for just one second to say something a",
        "start": 548.26,
        "duration": 5.34
    },
    {
        "text": "little bit more than just: \"Happy birthday.\"",
        "start": 553.6,
        "duration": 3.01
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 556.61,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Wish them that little bit extra that makes\nit more meaningful.",
        "start": 557.61,
        "duration": 3.17
    },
    {
        "text": "So, if it's someone's birthday, you could\nsay after that: \"I wish you\" or \"We wish you\",",
        "start": 560.78,
        "duration": 7.9
    },
    {
        "text": "depending on the situation...",
        "start": 568.68,
        "duration": 1.35
    },
    {
        "text": "\"I wish you a __________ year ahead.\"",
        "start": 570.03,
        "duration": 3.52
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, what could you say here?",
        "start": 573.55,
        "duration": 2.28
    },
    {
        "text": "All kinds of things.",
        "start": 575.83,
        "duration": 1.85
    },
    {
        "text": "Personalize it, depending on who you're talking\nto.",
        "start": 577.68,
        "duration": 2.07
    },
    {
        "text": "Right?",
        "start": 579.75,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "You could say: \"I wish you a wonderful year\nahead.\"",
        "start": 580.75,
        "duration": 2.9
    },
    {
        "text": "Very general.",
        "start": 583.65,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "\"I wish you a beautiful year ahead.\", \"I wish\nyou an exceptional year ahead.\", \"I wish you",
        "start": 584.65,
        "duration": 5.04
    },
    {
        "text": "a brilliant year ahead.\", \"I wish you a successful\nyear ahead.\"",
        "start": 589.69,
        "duration": 4.39
    },
    {
        "text": "In business, that's a very common greeting\nand a very nice wish for someone: \"I wish",
        "start": 594.08,
        "duration": 4.531
    },
    {
        "text": "you a very successful year ahead.\"",
        "start": 598.611,
        "duration": 2.459
    },
    {
        "text": "And if it's somebody that you're really close\nto, you can add on various adjectives: \"I",
        "start": 601.07,
        "duration": 5.64
    },
    {
        "text": "wish you a happy, healthy, and prosperous\nyear ahead.\"",
        "start": 606.71,
        "duration": 3.8
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 610.51,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "You don't have to say just one thing; you\ncan say many things.",
        "start": 611.51,
        "duration": 3.55
    },
    {
        "text": "All right?",
        "start": 615.06,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "But it's good to try to say something more\nthan just the basic: \"Happy birthday.\"",
        "start": 616.06,
        "duration": 5.99
    },
    {
        "text": "All right?",
        "start": 622.05,
        "duration": 1.2
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay.",
        "start": 623.25,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Next, for someone's wedding, what else could\nyou say after: \"Congratulations\"?",
        "start": 624.25,
        "duration": 4.56
    },
    {
        "text": "You could say: \"We wish you lots of happiness.\",\n\"We wish you a lifetime of joy together.\"",
        "start": 628.81,
        "duration": 7.69
    },
    {
        "text": "Something like that.",
        "start": 636.5,
        "duration": 1.8
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 638.3,
        "duration": 1.12
    },
    {
        "text": "Next, for a new job or somebody gets a promotion,\nyou could say the same thing: \"I wish you",
        "start": 639.42,
        "duration": 6.26
    },
    {
        "text": "lots of success.\"",
        "start": 645.68,
        "duration": 1.68
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 647.36,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Success\" is a good word to use around...",
        "start": 648.36,
        "duration": 2.53
    },
    {
        "text": "For academic achievements, for professional\nachievements, anything like that; a little",
        "start": 650.89,
        "duration": 4.66
    },
    {
        "text": "bit more formal.",
        "start": 655.55,
        "duration": 1.95
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 657.5,
        "duration": 1.36
    },
    {
        "text": "And exams, someone tells you that they've\ndone very well and you say: \"Congratulations!",
        "start": 658.86,
        "duration": 4.15
    },
    {
        "text": "Fantastic!",
        "start": 663.01,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "I knew you could do it!\"",
        "start": 664.01,
        "duration": 1.47
    },
    {
        "text": "All right?",
        "start": 665.48,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Something like that; something very encouraging.",
        "start": 666.48,
        "duration": 1.77
    },
    {
        "text": "All right.",
        "start": 668.25,
        "duration": 1.63
    },
    {
        "text": "In a...",
        "start": 669.88,
        "duration": 1.62
    },
    {
        "text": "In a difficult situation-someone suffers a\nloss, someone passes away-you could say: \"I'm",
        "start": 671.5,
        "duration": 5.67
    },
    {
        "text": "so sorry for your loss.\"",
        "start": 677.17,
        "duration": 1.89
    },
    {
        "text": "Again, we talked about: \"My condolences.\"",
        "start": 679.06,
        "duration": 4.26
    },
    {
        "text": "And also, we didn't talk about this before,\nbut if somebody's just ill-okay?-you could",
        "start": 683.32,
        "duration": 5.1
    },
    {
        "text": "say, first of all: \"Get well soon.\"",
        "start": 688.42,
        "duration": 3.06
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 691.48,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "And then in both of these situations of a\nloss or illness, you could add something personal,",
        "start": 692.48,
        "duration": 4.98
    },
    {
        "text": "like: \"Please let me know\" or \"Please let\nus know if we can help in some way.\", \"Please",
        "start": 697.46,
        "duration": 5.55
    },
    {
        "text": "let me know how I can help.\", \"Please let\nme know what I can do to help you.\"",
        "start": 703.01,
        "duration": 4.76
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 707.77,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Just say the word.\"",
        "start": 708.77,
        "duration": 1.62
    },
    {
        "text": "Something like that.",
        "start": 710.39,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 711.39,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "You could write it or say it.",
        "start": 712.39,
        "duration": 3.19
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, when it comes to: \"Thanks\" and \"Thank\nyou\", again, try to make it more meaningful.",
        "start": 715.58,
        "duration": 6.18
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 721.76,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Don't just say: \"Thank you.\"",
        "start": 722.76,
        "duration": 1.43
    },
    {
        "text": "Thank you for what?",
        "start": 724.19,
        "duration": 1.24
    },
    {
        "text": "Tell them.",
        "start": 725.43,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 726.43,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Thanks for\"...",
        "start": 727.43,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Or: \"Thank you\", okay?",
        "start": 728.43,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Thank you for your help.\", \"Thanks for your\nsupport.\", \"Thanks for your kindness.\", \"Thank",
        "start": 729.43,
        "duration": 5.2
    },
    {
        "text": "you for your encouragement, your generosity.\",\n\"Thank you for your business.\"",
        "start": 734.63,
        "duration": 4.98
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 739.61,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "That's very important if you're writing to\na customer or a client: \"Thank you for...\"",
        "start": 740.61,
        "duration": 4.15
    },
    {
        "text": "Thank them for their business.",
        "start": 744.76,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 745.76,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "They have many choices; they chose you - thank\nthem.",
        "start": 746.76,
        "duration": 2.29
    },
    {
        "text": "Let them know why you're thanking them.",
        "start": 749.05,
        "duration": 2.42
    },
    {
        "text": "And you can write it like this, by using the\nnoun.",
        "start": 751.47,
        "duration": 3.1
    },
    {
        "text": "You could say: \"Thank you for your help\",\nor you could just say: \"Thank you for helping",
        "start": 754.57,
        "duration": 4.03
    },
    {
        "text": "me.\", \"Thank you for being so kind.\", \"Thank\nyou for being so generous.\", \"Thank you for",
        "start": 758.6,
        "duration": 6.34
    },
    {
        "text": "being so encouraging.\"",
        "start": 764.94,
        "duration": 2.38
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 767.32,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "All kinds of things like that.",
        "start": 768.32,
        "duration": 1.79
    },
    {
        "text": "And I am genuinely saying to you: Thank you\nfor watching engVid, and thank you so much",
        "start": 770.11,
        "duration": 5.89
    },
    {
        "text": "for subscribing-I hope-to my YouTube channel.",
        "start": 776.0,
        "duration": 2.96
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 778.96,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "So you can continue to get lots of useful,\npractical lessons to help you improve your",
        "start": 779.96,
        "duration": 4.85
    },
    {
        "text": "English.",
        "start": 784.81,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "And most of all, I want to say congratulations\nto you for taking ownership and taking control",
        "start": 785.81,
        "duration": 7.3
    },
    {
        "text": "of your English.",
        "start": 793.11,
        "duration": 1.04
    },
    {
        "text": "All right?",
        "start": 794.15,
        "duration": 1.02
    },
    {
        "text": "I really admire you.",
        "start": 795.17,
        "duration": 1.6
    },
    {
        "text": "So, if you'd like to take this one step further,\nplease visit our website at www.engvid.com.",
        "start": 796.77,
        "duration": 6.49
    },
    {
        "text": "There, you can do a quiz on this and really\npractice these expressions so they flow easily,",
        "start": 803.26,
        "duration": 6.51
    },
    {
        "text": "because as I said, in the most important times\nwhich are happy times or sad times, you want",
        "start": 809.77,
        "duration": 6.19
    },
    {
        "text": "to know that you know exactly what to say\nand you want it to come smoothly and easily",
        "start": 815.96,
        "duration": 4.89
    },
    {
        "text": "from your mouth.",
        "start": 820.85,
        "duration": 1.4
    },
    {
        "text": "Okay?",
        "start": 822.25,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Thanks very much for watching.",
        "start": 823.25,
        "duration": 1.279
    },
    {
        "text": "Bye for now, and all the best with your English.",
        "start": 824.529,
        "duration": 1.931
    },
    {
        "text": "Bye.",
        "start": 826.46,
        "duration": 0.28
    }
]